works.description: After its launch in the UAE lately, European air purifier brand Airfree has collaborated with Galeries Lafayette, Dubai. Airfree is now exhibiting its limited edition S-Exclusiv range at the leading Parisian departmental store. The three Swarovski-studded models, the first in the company’s Limited Edition S-Exclusiv range, are exclusive to Galeries Lafayette and are now available to the customers.
